## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `npm run build` to verify no TypeScript issues.
- Verify the backend API returns valid JSON when fed a dummy base64 image.

### Manual Verification
- Add a dummy `GEMINI_API_KEY` locally.
- Click "Scan Receipt" in the web browser -> it should open the web file picker/webcam.
- Build the APK, tap the button -> it should open the Android Camera, take a picture, and pop up the Add dialog 3-4 seconds later perfectly pre-filled.
